          <h3>Overview</h3>
          <p>Fringely is a forum about women’s hair, specifically bangs, inspired by my time working as a hair stylist. In the hair industry, stylists refer to bangs as “fringe”, which is the root word of the forum’s name, Fringely.</p> 

          <p>This web application was written in Ruby and runs on the Sinatra framework. I wrote SQL commands to make queries to the Postgres database, which stores user’s login information, passwords, posts, topics, likes, and comments.</p>
