          <h3>Creating Functionality</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Custom coded forms for login, sign up, post creation, and comments</li>
            <li>A user can create an account and log in. The password is encrypted through Bcrypt. Her posts and comments are associated with her account.</li>
            <li>A user cannot comment or post without logging in</li>
            <li>Any visitor to Fringely can “like” a post</li>
            <li>Through the gem Redcarpet, the user can write her posts in Markdown and have them displayed in HTML on the forum.</li>
            <li>Fringely’s top posts are displayed on the index page based on popularity from “likes” and sorted by an SQL command.</li>
            <li>Posts are also sorted and displayed by the topic they are posted under.</li>
          </ul>  
