          <h3>Designing the User Experience and Layout</h3>
          <p>When I designed the look and feel of Fringely, I had the user in mind. I pictured my clients from the salon, who were in high school or right out of college, using this forum. I thought that Fringely should have a trendy, bold, and high fashion feel to it, but still be youthful and fun. I chose a black, white and grey color scheme and used Google fonts Oswald and Cabin Condensed to achieve the look. The layout is on Skeleton’s grid system.</p>
